flowchart TD
  A{Active threat actor activity now?} -->|Yes| B[Stabilize comms<br/>Start incident log]
  B --> C[Preserve quickly<br/>EDR export; firewall/VPN/auth logs]
  C --> D[Isolate affected hosts<br/>EDR containment; port shutdown; VLAN quarantine]
  D --> E[Stop known bad<br/>Block IOCs; disable confirmed compromised accounts]
  E --> F[Do NOT mass-reimage or wipe<br/>until DFIR confirms evidence is sufficient]

  A -->|No / Unknown| G[Preserve logs/telemetry first]
  G --> H[Increase monitoring for key signals]
  H --> I[Scoped containment<br/>Reset passwords; revoke tokens; remove persistence]

  I --> J{Account compromise suspected?}
  F --> J
  J -->|Yes| K[Collect auth logs first<br/>Then reset/disable accounts<br/>Revoke sessions/tokens; remove suspicious OAuth apps]
  J -->|No| L[Continue monitoring + targeted containment]

  K --> M{Ransomware indicators?}
  L --> M
  M -->|Yes| N[Isolate segments/hosts<br/>Preserve ransom note + EDR details<br/>Validate backups before restore]
  M -->|No| O[Proceed]

  N --> P{Public-facing system compromise?}
  O --> P
  P -->|Yes| Q[Capture state<br/>Snapshot/image/configs/logs<br/>Consider takedown/WAF rules]
  P -->|No| R[Proceed]

  Q --> S{Sensitive data potentially accessed?<br/>PII / PHI / CJIS / financial}
  R --> S
  S -->|Yes| T[Engage leadership + legal/IR vendor + insurance<br/>Use holding statement template]
  S -->|No| U[Document actions + continue recovery planning]
